<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-4910] groovy.bat fails when the JAVA_OPTS contains space characters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4910</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;groovy.bat fails when the JAVA_OPTS environment variable contains space characters like the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; set JAVA_OPTS=-Daprop=&quot;a value&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; bin\groovy -h&lt;br/&gt;
value&quot;&quot; was unexpected at this time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
